# Frontend Design

Promoted from `.agents/rules/frontend.md` (condensed). Pairs with `component-standards.mdc`.

## Layout

- 4px grid only — no arbitrary spacing
- High density: table cells max `py-2 px-4`
- List pages: `mb-8` between overview → toolbar → table

## Visual

- Semantic pastels for state encoding only
- Dark: `#0B0F19` base, `#111827` surface — no pure black
- Shadows only on floating elements (modals, dropdowns)
- Financial numbers: `.tabular-nums`

## Interaction

- Table rows clickable → `FullScreenWorkspace`
- `Esc` closes FSW
- No static Actions column when row click opens detail
